glosses: A municipality of Tavastia Proper, Finland.
completely; used as intensifier with the adverb yksin (“alone”)

words.etymology_text: A reduplicated formation built on yksin; compare täpötäysi and others listed there. The reduplicant ypö was later treated as a separate word and elaborated to ypösen.

glosses: from, related or pertaining to Ypäjä

forms.form: Rare. Only used with substantive adjectives.

glosses: a person from or living in Ypäjä
